<template>
   <v-container fluid>
    <SearchBar/>
       <!-- <v-btn @click="showList">give list</v-btn> -->
    <v-card 
    v-for="form in list_of_forms" :key="form"
    @click="renderSpecs"
    max-width="344"
    outlined
    hover
    class="mx-auto card-white-space card-overflow-wrap"
    >
    <v-card-title>{{ form }}</v-card-title>
    </v-card>
 
   </v-container>
</template>
<script>
import SearchBar from './SearchBar';
export default {
    name: 'AllForms',
    components:{
        SearchBar
    },
    props:['connection', 'sendMessage', 'connected'],

    data: () =>{
    return {
      list_of_forms: [],
    } },
    methods: {
        showList:function(){
            console.log(this.list_of_forms)
        },
        renderSpecs(){}
    },
    created: function(){
      this.connection.onmessage = (message) =>{
    //   this.list_of_forms = message.data;
      this.list_of_forms = JSON.parse("[" + message.data + "]")[0];
      console.log('onmessage',this.list_of_forms);
      }
    },
    watch:{
      connected: function(){
            this.sendMessage('Hello')
        }
    }
}
</script>

</style>
